Dice up a few @roma tomatoes{}.

Add the tomatoes, @dried basil{}, @garlic{}, @balsamic vinegar{}, @olive oil{}, @lentils{}, and @salt{} to a #bowl{}.

Give it a toss and let that marinate for at least ~{10%minutes}.

Then crumble in @feta cheese{} and top with @arugula{}.

Optional: pair with @grilled chicken{2%ounces} added protein.
